RaeLyn is a highly dependable HR resource and was always able to provide expert advice and options whenever dealing with any sort of HR related issue.  She was extremely helpful when looking to acquire new talent to add to the Operations team and invaluable in some of the less enjoyable times when dealing with employee issues.  Raelyn has always been able to remain a highly approachable HR resource, who employees truly considered a teammate.  This characteristic can be extremely critical whenever undergoing any sort of merger/acquisition.  She has always been a dedicated, loyal, compassionate colleague and I look forward to the opportunity to work with her again.
